PRACTICAL MAP

- Use `*_hist.root` and `nu_selection*.root` when you want flat TTrees and
  per-event/per-subrun analysis variables.
- Use `%ifb_%tc_*.root` when you want persisted art event products for later
  processing stages.
- Use the `ImageProduct` sparse vectors to rebuild image pixels.
- Use `inf_n_scores` to unflatten `inf_scores`.
